<p>其中：<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>F</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">CF</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">F</span></span></span></span>为转换因子；<br>
